thread.title: Ben Beveridge
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Ben Beveridge

author: Ben Beveridge
title: Ben Beveridge
text: Store dj has a great and helpful staff who will help you pick out any gear you require. In my experience, the guy I bought a midi controller from decoded to give me a discount after spending many moments trying to pick out te perfect keyboard with him. Store dj also has an incredibly wide range of products.
